description: A security flaw has been discovered in iPynch Social Network Website up to b6933b6d7f82c84819abe458ccf0e59d61119541. The affected element is an unknown function of the component Search. Performing manipulation results in sql injection. The attack is possible to be carried out remotely. The exploit has been released to the public and may be exploited. This product adopts a rolling release strategy to maintain continuous delivery
